Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&H9090A1&\4a&HC7&}.{\3c\3a\4c\4a}减七       {\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&H9090A1&\4a&HC7&}.{\3c\3a\4c\4a}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&H9090A1&\4a&HC7&}.{\3c\3a\4c\4a}减七和弦{\3c&H000000&\3a&HFF&\4c&H9090A1&\4a&HC7&}.{\3c\3a\4c\4a}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,来看这个简单的和弦进行\N{\fs36}Here's a simple chord progression.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,听上去不错，但如果我们想让它听起来更加变化时应该怎样呢？\N{\fs36}That works just fine, but what if we want to spice this up with a little more movement?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一个简单的做法就是在中间插入一个减七和弦\N{\fs36}Well, one easy way of doing that is to throw in a diminished seventh chord.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.94,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,210)\fs32}（不要和半减七和弦搞混）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一个{\b1}减减七和弦{\b0}，或者叫{\b1}减七和弦{\b0\fs32}（也叫{\b1}减导七和弦{\b0}）{\fs}，\N{\fs36}A fully diminished seventh chord, or just "diminished seventh chord" for short,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.67,0:00:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,结构上即在根音上方叠加三个小三度\N{\fs36}is the structure we get when we stack three minor 3rds on top of a root note.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,减七和弦听起来黑暗且不稳定\N{\fs36}Diminished seventh chords sound extremely dark and unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这些特性很有用——\N{\fs36}This means they're actually really useful –
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用它来创造有很强期待感的解决\N{\fs36}we can use them to create a strong expectation of resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想象把一个减七和弦作为目标，或者导向一个别的主要和弦\N{\fs36}Think of the diminished seventh chord as a way of targeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,想象把一个减七和弦作为目标，或者导向一个别的主要和弦\N{\fs36}or leading into certain other chords.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,最常见的形式就是用减七和弦来解决到其向上半音的和弦\N{\fs36}The most common pattern for diminished seventh chords is to resolve up a half-step.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们再看一次这个进行\N{\fs36}Here's that progression of ours again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们试着插入一个减七和弦来导向 E 小和弦\N{\fs36}So let's try inserting a diminished seventh chord that leads up a half-step into the E- chord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这个例子中，导向减七和弦的和弦也刚巧是向上半音解决到我们的减七和弦\N{\fs36}In this particular case, we also happen to be approaching the diminished seventh chord
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这个例子中，导向减七和弦的和弦也刚巧是向上半音解决到我们的减七和弦\N{\fs36}itself with half-step up motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你并不总需要这样做，不过这样听起来的确不错\N{\fs36}You don't always have to do it this way, but it does tend to work really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个有效的减七和弦模式是向下解决半音\N{\fs36}Another effective diminished seventh chord pattern is resolving down a half-step.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,举个例子\N{\fs36}Here's an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也可以使用减七和弦来导向同主音的其它和弦\N{\fs36}We can also approach a chord with a diminished seventh chord built on the same root note.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这在一级{\fs32}（主和弦）{\fs}和五级和弦{\fs32}（属和弦）{\fs}中效果更为显著\N{\fs36}This works especially well on the I and V chords.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,被称为{\b1}辅助减七和弦{\b0\fs32}（{\b1}同音共减七和弦{\b0}）{\fs}\N{\fs36}These are called auxiliary diminished seventh chords.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个不错的延时方案用以导向目标和弦，\N{\fs36}This is a great technique for delaying resolution to the target chord,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以以这种独特形式用来为缓慢的进行添加额外动作\N{\fs36}or creating extra harmonic motion in an otherwise static moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可见，减七和弦有诸多用途非常实用\N{\fs36}So, fully diminished seventh chords are really versatile and useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,它构成的紧张听感使得其导向的和弦听起来更悦耳\N{\fs36}Their extremely tense sound makes the relief of the following chord feel that much sweeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当然这里只是一个向你展示无限可能性的一个小小介绍\N{\fs36}As always, this is a merely an introduction to a whole world of possibilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就试试你能够使用它来创造出什么吧\N{\fs36}so get experimenting and see what you can come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是一些写作提示以边你上手\N{\fs36}Here's a little writing prompt to get you started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,编写一个任意风格的和弦进行\N{\fs36}Write a chord progression in any style.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,使之至少有 8 小节长度，但如果你想的话多长都可以\N{\fs36}Make it at least 8 bars long, but feel free to go as long as you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,然后试着包含如下至少一个减七和弦模式\N{\fs36}and try to include at least one of each diminished seventh chord pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想要的话，你也可以加上旋律和额外的改编\N{\fs36}You can add a melody and additional arrangement if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们主要目的还是去感受这些和弦本身\N{\fs36}but the main idea here is just to get a feel for the chords themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的作品发到评论区这样大家就都能看看了{\fs36}\N\N\NPost whatever you come up with in the comments so we can all take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的，分享点子嘛...也许我们能够互相学到一些东西...{\fs36}\N\N\NYou know, we're sharing ideas...maybe we're learning a thing or two from each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会很棒\N{\fs36}it's gonna be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你喜欢这个视频请（在油管）订阅我的频道\N{\fs36}If you enjoyed this video, please subscribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也别忘了看看我的 Patreon 页面\N{\fs36}Also check out my Patreon page.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这个频道的目的是向世界提供免费的音乐教学视频\N{\fs36}The purpose of this channel is to offer free music education to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你的贡献能使之成为可能\N{\fs36}and your contributions make that possible.
